  "prompt": "What is Yelp?",
  "response": "Yelp is a popular online platform and mobile application that connects people with local businesses, primarily focusing on restaurants, but also including other services like retail, home services, and more. Users can search for businesses, read and write reviews, view photos, and get information on business hours, locations, and contact details. Yelp also offers features such as reservations, food delivery, and the ability to request quotes from service providers. The platform helps users make informed decisions about where to spend their money and helps businesses gain visibility and attract new customers.",
